Willie Edward DOZIER, Petitioner, v. The STATE of Florida, Respondent. No. 42111. Supreme Court of Florida. May 10, 1972. ROBERTS, C. J., and CARLTON, ADKINS, BOYD and DEKLE, JJ., concur. ERVIN and McCAIN, JJ., dissent.

Rehearing Denied June 30, 1972.

Certiorari denied. 257 So.2d 49.
